      • executeAndReport

        <R> CompletableFuture<MultiEntityOperationExecutionReport<R>> executeAndReport​(EntityReferenceFactory<R> entityReferenceFactory)
        Writes all pending changes to the index now, and clears the plan so that it can be re-used.
        Type Parameters:
        R - The type of entity references in the returned execution report.
        Parameters:
        entityReferenceFactory - A factory for entity references in the returned execution report.
        Returns:
        A CompletableFuture that will be completed with an execution report when all the works are complete.

        The serialized form of the provided identifier.
